PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772052053
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told storm drain
OL,4,C'could be easily opened'
OL,6,FThe jury inquest at Belfast Coroner's
OL,7,FCourt is now in its fifth week.
OL,9,FSean McCarry, the regional commander
OL,10,Ffor the Community Rescue Service
OL,11,F(CRS), said a team of trained
OL,12,Fvolunteers were deployed to the
OL,13,FNorthwood Road area after being
OL,14,Falerted that Noah's bicycle had been
OL,15,Fdiscovered.
OL,17,FThe area was searched and a culvert
OL,18,Fwas found on waste ground located at
OL,19,Fthe back of some houses.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772052053
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told storm drain
OL,4,C'could be easily opened'
OL,6,FIn his statement, Mr McCarry said the
OL,7,Fsearchers spotted that the grill on
OL,8,Fthe top of it "was unlocked and could
OL,9,Fbe easily opened".
OL,11,FThe volunteers suggested the culvert
OL,12,Fshould be searched as they felt that
OL,13,Fan adult could pass through it.
OL,15,FHe said he made contact and stated it
OL,16,Fwas "easy to get into" the culvert and
OL,17,Fit needed searching by a confined
OL,18,Fspace trained and equipped team.
OL,26,@pD@OOUqD@QO]xD@EOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
