PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772052053
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told storm drain
OL,4,C'could be easily opened'
OL,6,FHe added: "From early on we were aware
OL,7,Fof this as a potential ingress point
OL,8,Fas it was possible for one our
OL,9,Ftechnicians who was of slim build to
OL,10,Fpass between the bars."
OL,12,FAt least 100 community search and
OL,13,Frescue volunteers were called out to
OL,14,Fthe Cavehill area, which had been the
OL,15,Finitial focus of the search for Noah.
OL,17,FUpdated information made the search
OL,18,Ffor the missing youngster "fluid", the
OL,19,Fcourt heard.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@WO]zD@[OUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
