CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772052053
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told storm drain
OL,4,C'could be easily opened'
OL,6,FIt included a call to deploy searchers
OL,7,Fin the North Queen Street are where a
OL,8,Fphone was found.
OL,10,FPolice then contacted Mr McCarry in
OL,11,Fthe early evening to say Noah's
OL,12,Fbicycle was found in Northwood Road.
OL,14,FMr McCarry said the search team of
OL,15,Fvolunteers are often called out to
OL,16,FCavehill and are familiar with its
OL,17,Fdense terrain, which he said included
OL,18,Fpassable areas but "the rest is
OL,19,Fsometimes like the jungle".
OL,26,@zD@TOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
