PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772052053
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told storm drain
OL,4,C'could be easily opened'
OL,6,FEarlier jurors watched a BBC
OL,7,Fdocumentary about the work of the
OL,8,Fsearch team who tried to find Noah
OL,9,Fagainst the backdrop of the covid
OL,10,Flockdown.
OL,12,FIt showed the heart warming response
OL,13,Fof the North Belfast community who
OL,14,Fcame out of their homes in large
OL,15,Fnumbers in an effort to help find him.
OL,17,FCRS volunteers described the search as
OL,18,F"relentless" and with a "real sense of
OL,19,Furgency" as bushes, dense thickets and
OL,20,Fwater were searched in the hunt to
OL,21,Ffind the boy.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@LO]zD@YOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
