OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest told storm drain
OL,4,C'could be easily opened'
OL,6,FNoah's mother Fiona Donohoe recalled
OL,7,Fit was a "horrible" period.
OL,9,FShe said: "He got on his bike and I
OL,10,Fwas able to hug him and tell him I
OL,11,Floved him.
OL,13,F"I phoned and I knew if he wasn't
OL,14,Fanswering his phone something wasn't
OL,15,Fright."
